] The compositions of “NN‐predictions” and “high/low certainty predictions” refer to the optimized structures predicted by NN and GPR models. The overpotentials are calculated as the average of DFT calculation for the selected structures in Section 2.2.2 and the synthesis cost is calculated according to Equation (1).
